  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You take a boxers stance, when you are confronted by a melee attack from a creature within 5 feet of you.</p><p>Until the beginning of your next turn, each melee attack that targets you, you can spend 4 chakra. When you do, you attempt to duck and weave granting yourself a +2 Bonus to your AC against the triggering creature and then immediately make one unarmed attack in response to the triggering melee attack. This bonus to AC stacks up to twice.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank increase the activation cost of this jutsu by 3. If this jutsu is cast at B-Rank, increase the AC bonus by +1.</p>",
